  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_ci-fails.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">When the validation step in your CI pipeline fails, your pull request
