              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_ci-fails.dita" xtrc="b:4;50:18">Validate documentation</b> step, and read the output.</p>
              <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_ci-fails.dita" xtrc="p:4;51:18">Alternatively, if reports were uploaded as artifacts, download
